                    <h1>HOME</h1>
                    <p>Durasort Inc. is an ISO 9001:2000 registered company that has been providing cost effective quality services to automotive suppliers and other factory suppliers since 2002.  Our clients within the Automotive Industry include <b>World and North American Leaders in the Fastener Markets</b>. These customers rely on <b>Durasort as their Primary Production Sort and Package Supplier</b>. Durasort enhances the overall quality of their products while significantly reducing their rework and quality issue costs.  </p>
                    <p>With around the clock operations, Durasort Inspects approximately 2.5 Million pcs./day and Packages approximately 4 Million pcs./day.  This translates into 700 Million pcs. Sorted and Over 1 Billion pcs. Packaged annually.  We are highly responsive to our customers demand and Durasort ensures that our customer's product requirements are met daily.</p>
